I think we're having a bit of a déjà vu moment! As a conversational AI, I don't have personal experiences or memories, so I don't recall any interactions with Rachel or any previous conversations about books.

However, I'd be happy to help you find book recommendations similar to your favorite author or genre! Can you tell me more about your favorite author or the type of books you enjoy reading? That way, I can suggest some titles or authors that might interest you.

If you'd like to discuss books with Rachel, that's great too! Bookstores are fantastic places to meet fellow book lovers and get recommendations. Just remember that I'm a large language model, I don't have personal experiences or recall previous conversations. Each time you interact with me, it's a new conversation!
